														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1261536">
									

<p>And before people start asking the reverse question, due to the way TV dramas work, Blink would have to have been written before SCP-173 existed. (I'm not clear on the air dates, but I'm assuming Blink was first aired in the UK shortly after SCP-173 was put up on /x/.)</p>
<p>Convergent idea evolution. It happens.</p>

